{"tid":1135930,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"（認真L）決定改100首歌詞","createTime":"2019-05-02T15:56:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T10:51:26.000Z","uid":251706,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ac156f536b5e6733a1ee38c5e589f0dee4dab9cf","tid":1135930,"uid":251706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T15:56:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁多年黎，好似無咩俾過自己挑戰<br />\n今日心血來潮，決定改夠100首歌詞<br />\n<br />\n做人有決心，似乎唔係一件好容易既事<br />\n所以開個post黎決志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算寫得唔夠動人，寫得唔夠好<br />\n都算有努力過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又認真L模式啟動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3814ae87bcc7f937ece5ab50f0431fbad3cfe29b","tid":1135930,"uid":251706,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T15:58:00.000Z","msg":"#1 <br />\n改自 麥浚龍 - 雷克雅未克<br />\n<br />\n《真實的虛謊》<br />\n<br />\n巫師有美妙法力 可以讓你覺醒<br />\n各種規矩完美  約束多少人性<br />\n從來憑著制度定<br />\n決定來夜與誰看星<br />\n而我看到你<br />\n靈魂裡獨自憐影<br />\n<br />\n毒蠍毒液若飲清<br />\n生死的過後 靈就能甦醒<br />\n回復眼神心性 來提示 神的心聲 人間的足跡  <br />\n多少都靠著前事來決定<br />\n徬徨路人像你 難憑心的感應<br />\n<br />\n*想像裏透出燭光<br />\n盼望和誰渡過<br />\n但卻又覺得絕望<br />\n將眼淚完全釋放 <br />\n<br />\n真實裡太多虛謊<br />\n如若相信直覺<br />\n好比同行 得到極燦爛的曙光 忘掉迷茫<br />\n崎嶇目光 不需認錯*<br />\n<br />\n還是 會害怕 虛空之中<br />\n人的快樂如夢是場大放縱<br />\n走出一切定型 仿似 神聖的對沖    <br />\n<br />\n從來未抱擁 誰看著鏡內鏡像<br />\n不假思索去擁抱<br />\n或者心裡 總很掙扎 難以放鬆<br />\n披荊斬棘 苦行裡在痛哭<br />\n想將參差刪除 靈魂中來移除 來修正夢<br />\n靈魂中 來移除 誰的作弄<br />\n如靈魂中 能移除<br />\n人間少很多 精彩內容<br />\n為何未懂 臃腫觀念 跟著你<br />\n來回的 一直以後 你便你便退<br />\n讓美麗 葬在最深 白雪中<br />\n<br />\nrepeat*<br />\n<br />\n在這現實像孤星<br />\n心中的記號 誰又來記認<br />\n藏著哪能呼應<br />\n誰人在 旋律中傾聽 重複的掩飾<br />\n掩飾中盼望能自行鎮靜<br />\n然而並無自信 能防心甦醒希冀<br />\n<br />\n可有美妙法力 可以讓你覺醒<br />\n若果忠於靈性 去觸摸可能性<br />\n從來尋覓 要用情<br />\n美麗神殿也能破冰<br />\n誰也會經過 和最深的束縛爭執中決勝"},{"pid":"4bfcc9c34243e9a4be2789d6d54e779f8dc737cd","tid":1135930,"uid":251706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T16:02:54.000Z","msg":"漏左個&ldquo;縮&rdquo;字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n來回的 一直以後 你便你便退縮"},{"pid":"1eeca1fd0280bc2cb18168c4040177594cd23fd8","tid":1135930,"uid":153496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T16:37:14.000Z","msg":"個人覺得聽慣咗原詞就好難抽離<br />\n樓主加油"},{"pid":"45a131c8f603a88ff2991d0e80794af7605fc3ae","tid":1135930,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T16:40:51.000Z","msg":"我揀歌同主體比樓主作ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5b391cc36d5be4ec8d41c68b4ea3e2c434a6d3","tid":1135930,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T17:50:58.000Z","msg":"修行加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25bb8f17205534f03579091f5cbbb8c3d21c0f7c","tid":1135930,"uid":394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45a131c8f603a88ff2991d0e80794af7605fc3ae","tid":1135930,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T16:40:51.000Z","msg":"我揀歌同主體比樓主作ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T19:18:37.000Z","msg":"跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c16ddfcc1ebfe5d3fe71da827c56cb62ecd3903","tid":1135930,"uid":251706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45a131c8f603a88ff2991d0e80794af7605fc3ae","tid":1135930,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-